# DreamCo Technologies — Code Owners
# Every file and directory must have at least one owner.
# Owners are automatically requested as reviewers on pull requests.

# Global fallback — DreamCo core team owns everything by default
*                           @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team

# Core OS infrastructure
python_bots/core/           @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team
python_bots/orchestrator.py @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team
python_bots/governance/     @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team

# Platform layer
dreamco_platform/           @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team
dreamco_mcp_server.py       @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team
dreamco_sdk/                @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team

# CI/CD — must be reviewed by infrastructure team
.github/workflows/          @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team
.github/dependabot.yml      @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team

# Security-sensitive files
requirements.txt            @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team
SECURITY.md                 @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team

# Bots — coding agents reviewed by core team
bots/coding/                @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team

# Tests — everyone can submit tests, core team reviews
tests/                      @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team

# Documentation — open to all contributors
*.md                        @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team
docs/                       @DreamCo-Technologies/core-team
